{"tid":1319744,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"714 沙田遊行後，深藍家人幫示威者講說話","createTime":"2019-07-15T08:32:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T18:12:46.000Z","uid":12557,"like":303,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"31ac675fff96b69baf812b352bd59f1ed6e91a81","tid":1319744,"uid":12557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T08:32:52.000Z","msg":"我父母分別係深藍同淺藍立場<br />\n同好多巴打一樣就政見已經同屋企人嘈過無數次<br />\n好多次都嘈到我老婆提議搬走，不過一來要人幫手照顧BB<br />\n二來經濟負擔會重好多<br />\n三來就算政見唔同我都愛我屋企人<br />\n唯有平時唔岩聽當聽唔到，自己又出少句聲<br />\n不過有時聽到佢睇新聞果時不停屌班示威者<br />\n又話一定收左錢，專登攪事，最好拉哂佢<br />\n講好多好難聽嘅野我都忍唔住會頂返佢<br />\n<br />\n佢兩個就已經退左休，半近年因為親戚係沙田間餐廳唔夠人<br />\n佢地就去左幫手做收銀<br />\n琴晚返到黎之後，佢兩個竟然主動同我講其實班後生仔都幾好，唔似係壞人，原來佢地話琴日親眼係餐廳見到d 示威者又好禮貌又守規矩，清場後入到餐廳唔識嘅人係度互相幫助，對話內容聽得出知道大家明顯唔係收錢攪事，唔係咩所謂有組織動員破壞，而係一班高質素嘅普通年青人因為意念相同而齊心合力<br />\n跟住佢地問我點解呢班人係新聞睇出黎咁暴力<br />\n佢地竟然好有心機咁聽我解釋哂，咩係和理非咩係勇武<br />\n點解有班人要勇武，同埋新聞剩係會播d 衝擊片段<br />\n其實大部份人同大部份時間都係和理非，不過因為新聞價值唔高，所以只會出現幾秒，反而之後d 衝突因為多人想睇一定會被人放大，就好似睇足球精華片咁<br />\n佢地聽完之後嘅口風大約係話其實兩邊都好同情<br />\n最衰都係政府逼警察出黎同示威者香港人打香港人<br />\n可能大家覺得呢句說話好普通，但係係我深藍嘅屋企人口中，我之前解釋過無數次都冇用，竟然咁樣可以令佢地明白，唔好話變黃，佢地都係對武力好反感，但係起碼由深藍變中立，我都忍唔住滴左兩滴眼淚，我好感謝大家，都好自豪大家都咁高質素，呢樣野係我對香港未絕望嘅唯一原因，多謝大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c16f7e2d875db68d04d41d25e7870ef83b1578a3","tid":1319744,"uid":12557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T08:37:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"642828cd85970d7d7f39fd3dc6d0e14e103b23e4","tid":1319744,"uid":46758,"like":43,"dislike":0,"score":43,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T08:39:53.000Z","msg":"落場一次就知咩事"},{"pid":"8fdf4f7a1361195d523a3eda76402d2a794aedef","tid":1319744,"uid":267328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"642828cd85970d7d7f39fd3dc6d0e14e103b23e4","tid":1319744,"uid":46758,"like":43,"dislike":0,"score":43,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T08:39:53.000Z","msg":"落場一次就知咩事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T08:40:21.000Z","msg":"真"},{"pid":"2757f04f48b2ce902cc30fb5eec8e9458d9d2218","tid":1319744,"uid":267328,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"c16f7e2d875db68d04d41d25e7870ef83b1578a3","tid":1319744,"uid":12557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T08:37:23.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T08:40:57.000Z","msg":"巴打, 黎緊佢地果兩票就靠你了, 加油!"},{"pid":"d7b5b80fab77054ece1fa809cae01ee0208bf66b","tid":1319744,"uid":10509,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T08:41:19.000Z","msg":"好多野 落現場睇一次就知"},{"pid":"88c60320dda8a98255f0335a2236da827ea3444c","tid":1319744,"uid":227811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T08:41:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"30998f15a4142a46d46598432e0734529fda6148","tid":1319744,"uid":19126,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T08:41:59.000Z","msg":"我好明樓豬個感受，我都有一個深藍既親戚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b38d99cf232f95d921a406f1b5e8ab2a05e75624","tid":1319744,"uid":51470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T08:42:34.000Z","msg":"羨慕你"},{"pid":"416af381a98cf0efb355d12195ef171731955f4f","tid":1319744,"uid":12557,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"d7b5b80fab77054ece1fa809cae01ee0208bf66b","tid":1319744,"uid":10509,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T08:41:19.000Z","msg":"好多野 落現場睇一次就知"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T08:56:47.000Z","msg":"其實如果可以嘅，可以帶d 俾新聞影響左嘅家人去現場睇下，叫佢地遠距離睇下就知咩事<br />\n當然係安全情況下，包括唔好去到屌尻d 示威者，同埋最好早d 去，係和理非未完之前走，當然現場睇埋d 黑警嘅暴行就最好，睇下佢地係點樣屈鳩d 示威者衝擊，不過老人家都怕佢地受傷所以最好唔好"},{"pid":"f380991cc5df4aa5d04a06dd89ca5e95b473eb82","tid":1319744,"uid":126087,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T08:57:10.000Z","msg":"羨慕你有肯聽你解釋嗰屋企人<br />\n我父母都係深藍<br />\n基本上係反對反對派<br />\n又係成日話啲示威者係收錢搞事<br />\n我有嘗試向佢地解釋<br />\n不過佢地啲反對反對派思想太根深蒂固<br />\n最後我都係放棄<br />\n係屋企唔同佢地講政治嘢<br />\n聽到佢地睇新聞屌示威者就忍下<br />\n為咗唔嘈交<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有時講啲歪理<br />\n我已經係屌都費事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我最奇怪嘅係<br />\n屋企已經係唔睇cctvb 係睇now tv<br />\n反而佢地識得話now tv偏頗<br />\n報導立場都有啲反中<br />\n扮到好客觀睇新聞咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ca31f681c74bbff6808ae5f8284f9d4bc282cf5","tid":1319744,"uid":132896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T08:58:25.000Z","msg":"睇到毛管棟<br />\n<br />\n大家加油"},{"pid":"46d05745fd39d6669bdd5eb4b45420d74d6fff1b","tid":1319744,"uid":18959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T08:59:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4384140c73f70e8a62355a1de8b7caec6cad8fe3","tid":1319744,"uid":12557,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"f380991cc5df4aa5d04a06dd89ca5e95b473eb82","tid":1319744,"uid":126087,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T08:57:10.000Z","msg":"羨慕你有肯聽你解釋嗰屋企人<br />\n我父母都係深藍<br />\n基本上係反對反對派<br />\n又係成日話啲示威者係收錢搞事<br />\n我有嘗試向佢地解釋<br />\n不過佢地啲反對反對派思想太根深蒂固<br />\n最後我都係放棄<br />\n係屋企唔同佢地講政治嘢<br />\n聽到佢地睇新聞屌示威者就忍下<br />\n為咗唔嘈交<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有時講啲歪理<br />\n我已經係屌都費事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我最奇怪嘅係<br />\n屋企已經係唔睇cctvb 係睇now tv<br />\n反而佢地識得話now tv偏頗<br />\n報導立場都有啲反中<br />\n扮到好客觀睇新聞咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T09:02:43.000Z","msg":"佢地之前都係同你父母一模一樣<br />\n跟本就冇得同佢地解釋<br />\n我都估唔到佢地親身接觸到示威者個效果可以咁強<br />\n不過都冇法，如果你冇親身係現場，剩係睇新聞<br />\n你都可能會同佢地有同樣結論"},{"pid":"cd5275be2f0b661bc97a1bf5400af294429a7b45","tid":1319744,"uid":12557,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T09:16:38.000Z","msg":"同時可能係和理非後勤做得太好<br />\n佢地成世人都未見過香港人可以咁團體<br />\n學習能力又咁高，咁快發展到一套手語，物流，資訊系統<br />\n完美分工合作<br />\n所以佢地會覺得係有組織訓練出黎"},{"pid":"42cad8f644eca073e55c243249aa3e1ed41fc680","tid":1319744,"uid":12557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T09:43:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"27b44d99d7dec39208d75a05ae6d51ac839d722f","tid":1319744,"uid":12557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T09:46:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"16e2a413b2e3bf5bbb1bc8f3a2a6cb60536acef3","tid":1319744,"uid":131121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T09:47:19.000Z","msg":"迷途知返"},{"pid":"b7ca497f03bfbad2582c4fb487173e675002d474","tid":1319744,"uid":240788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T09:49:12.000Z","msg":"唉我老豆幾時先生性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13e3eecd04976ac4e7b4d54d35d57410a50916d8","tid":1319744,"uid":180462,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T09:51:53.000Z","msg":"我發覺落場個時其實好多係勇武眼中on99既野對未落過場既人係好大既道德感召<br />\n例如人鏈呀 比掌聲自己 同路人講sorry<br />\n<br />\n但係佢地未必理解同知道到勇武背後既犧牲同理由 所以佢地眼中只會見到暴力 呢d反而係有認識既和理非先明"},{"pid":"4404248882e1b434031bd1a0f5e86b4d3211deb4","tid":1319744,"uid":259121,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T09:53:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6092d926f52b2fc4954d4d65c8c0cb5428b0ba00","tid":1319744,"uid":46534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T09:55:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f41de09c1ccc80f3e944ca0b5949219c22717fb7","tid":1319744,"uid":188859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30998f15a4142a46d46598432e0734529fda6148","tid":1319744,"uid":19126,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T08:41:59.000Z","msg":"我好明樓豬個感受，我都有一個深藍既親戚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T09:56:41.000Z","msg":"你都好丫，一個<br />\n<br />\n我一班呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abd37e247428c8dfd11a09927e6313760e0af736","tid":1319744,"uid":12557,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"13e3eecd04976ac4e7b4d54d35d57410a50916d8","tid":1319744,"uid":180462,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T09:51:53.000Z","msg":"我發覺落場個時其實好多係勇武眼中on99既野對未落過場既人係好大既道德感召<br />\n例如人鏈呀 比掌聲自己 同路人講sorry<br />\n<br />\n但係佢地未必理解同知道到勇武背後既犧牲同理由 所以佢地眼中只會見到暴力 呢d反而係有認識既和理非先明"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T09:57:41.000Z","msg":"我曾經都覺得嗌香港人加油果d好多餘<br />\n但係其實好多人係旁邊睇緊<br />\n我諗只要係香港人，聽到咁多人一齊嗌香港人加油<br />\n好難唔感動"},{"pid":"d92504713172c8821173bffd26e58f07e301064e","tid":1319744,"uid":240788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T09:58:07.000Z","msg":"屌可唔可以一齊屌鳩呢啲濕鳩page<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1320026\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1320026</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}